Package Bank

Class BankAccount

java.lang.Object
NumberManipulation.NumberGenerator
Bank.BankAccount
public class BankAccount extends NumberGenerator
Acts as VIEW/ADD ONLY Bank Account after the values are set they cannot be changed or manipulated only added upon. The constructor handles account number generation and formatting as well as inserting key value pairs into the map. The only things that need to be passed to the constructor are the person object, an array of bank types, and an array of bank values
